        <tr bgcolor="#DEDFDF">
          <td width="18%" valign="top"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><b>brien ZEP nyc</b></font></td>
          <td>
            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><font size="1" color="#000080" face="Verdana, Arial">posted 07-23-98 06:38 PM CT (US)</font></font>
            <hr>
            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">I was feeling a bit down in the dumps recently considering that I live in a LARGE urban center where you would think that there would be a lot of outlets for PEZ and I havn’t been able to locate any PEZ mini flashlights,bubble wands or key chains! Well oddly enough New York city is very limited when it comes to PEZ .But I did score today at lunch time as I was rummaging through the huge pile of PEZ in one of the many Jack’s 99 cent Stores. BINGO! There was a Garfield in Aviators Cap for a mere 99 cents to boot! Well needless to say that made my day. :=) Happy PEZzing.</font>
          </td>
        </tr>
