            <br>
            Something tells me that they'll be replacing the Garfield card stock that they use for the MOCs, too. But the Aviators that I found were all on the same old purple card. Maybe that'll make it more collectible -- new Garfield, old card.<br></font>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr bgcolor="#DEDFDF">
          <td width="18%" valign="top"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><b>Pezmanmike</b></font></td>
